{"root":{"data":{"id":"dh0oixst3t40","created":1773306034199,"text":"测试数据的几大原因"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0oncjdnq80","created":1773306379737,"text":"研究生阶段的能力铺垫","layout_mind_offset":{"x":38.333330584897254,"y":-26.499998639027666},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0p1qo7wps0","created":1773307507603,"text":"mems的使用练习，后续实验使用mems能够迅速上手","layout_right_offset":{"x":68.50000155965483,"y":-26.083334048174947}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0tr7sycbc0","created":1773320788439,"text":"分支主题","layout_right_offset":{"x":91.00000180800782,"y":0}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0onejsx5k0","created":1773306384116,"text":"加强毕设本身的理解","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-48.00000095367437,"y":93.00000184774422}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0ongf51wo0","created":1773306388188,"text":"实际技术需求","layout_mind_offset":{"x":874.0000139276212,"y":-164.75000299389205},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0ozlkz49k0","created":1773307339794,"text":"楼梯行走，除了x、y轴的轨迹变化还能观测z轴的轨\n迹变化，对z轴的轨迹解算也能有个验证（可以在楼\n梯行走的时候，穿插横向行走，同时检验y轴变化）","layout_right_offset":{"x":58.75000029181456,"y":38.75000019247352}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0oznr9vp40","created":1773307344529,"text":"变速折返跑（考虑到变速情况对零速检测\n的影响，同时折返时刻急停可能会误差）","layout_right_offset":{"x":63.7500003166499,"y":32.5000001614294}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0uf60heq80","created":1773322665280,"text":"圆形轨迹多圈验证，","layout_right_offset":{"x":72.5000003601117,"y":-176.25000087544362}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0vg6pebs00","created":1773325566260,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0up10yezc0","created":1773323438066,"text":"增加不同状态下的对比实验：我和上一个同学的步长\n不同，验证不同步长下的零速检测结果以及轨迹解算（检验算法对不同步长的适应能力，h）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0veukyr740","created":1773325461507,"text":"多步速对比实验","layout_right_offset":{"x":87.49999826153152,"y":-497.66662816869024}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0vf76wwrk0","created":1773325488955,"text":"复杂步态实验\n包含正常走、倒走、侧身走、爬行（如可行）、跳跃等多种步态模式的复合路径","layout_right_offset":{"x":88.33333157830802,"y":-503.16665953066746}},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}